Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍與聖母小姐的秘密？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.93,0:01:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.67,0:02:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個秘密就隱藏在\N島原發生的悲劇之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.34,0:02:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七十二話\N追憶的日子  翔伍與小夜的悲傷過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.78,0:02:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是翔伍大人 翔伍大人呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.16,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年前\N天草翔伍來到島原以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.93,0:02:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻統率所有天主教徒\N培育士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時也設立了孤兒院與醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.61,0:02:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是翔伍大人\N親自開的處方藥哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛苦一下子就減退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.59,0:02:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直不像真的\N身體變得輕鬆多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.53,0:03:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要早晚喝下這個藥\N不久以後身體就會復原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.10,0:03:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太感謝您了 太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是奇跡呀\N翔伍大人又創造奇跡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.97,0:03:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他治好絕癥病人了\N果然是天草四郎的轉世呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.68,0:03:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是神子呀\N翔伍大人要為我們創造神國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.15,0:03:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們終於\N可以脫離悲慘生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.42,0:03:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三百年來我們一直躲躲藏藏\N以後再也不必躲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望的國度要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天是聖靈的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.97,0:03:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要悼念14年前\N為村子殉教的人們的靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.81,0:03:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖靈的日子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.28,0:03:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是翔伍大人的父母親\N蒙主寵召的日子哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要在靈廟裏面閉關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.05,0:03:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也可以去嗎\N請讓我們一起祈禱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要祈禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.86,0:04:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 我們一起獻上祈禱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.30,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍為何可以治療病人\N預言天災地變呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是奇跡也不是魔術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.37,0:04:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是由於他在大陸城市\N學會西方醫學與天文學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本身知識淵博
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.25,0:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輕鬆就得到\N萬能救世主之名的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.39,0:04:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻有一個治不了的病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,治不了的病？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.26,0:04:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他妹妹聖母小姐生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.87,0:04:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且跟\N奪走他母親生命的病一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不治之癥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能夠動嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我作夢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純白的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.82,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天那一天又來臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.39,0:05:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸媽媽蒙主寵召的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.73,0:05:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.53,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島原在夢境裏面是白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都閃閃發亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.98,0:06:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家人在一起的最後一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天…又要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快來呀 小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.30,0:06:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽 你不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.38,0:06:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍 小夜 別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 你們先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.92,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.02,0:06:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神啊 請保佑我的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保佑我的家人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好了 翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.48,0:07:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸現在跟你講的事\N你終生都不可以忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大約250年來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島原居民一直瞞著幕府\N保有自己的信仰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是隱藏的天主教徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為心懷信仰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家才能夠\N忍受苛刻的勞動工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我盡己所能保護人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是神的教誨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.31,0:07:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人的靈魂都是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.11,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人的靈魂都是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神說：
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.42,0:07:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人活著的價值\N不在於身份與財富
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在於那心靈的高貴與美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.36,0:08:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我終生都不會拋棄這個教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我大概\N很快就會被逮捕判刑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.67,0:08:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好了\N你跟小夜就逃去大陸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今夜你叔叔兵衛會來接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就跟兵衛走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸跟媽媽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要變強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.99,0:08:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一天\N你會成為島原人民的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸把一切都托付給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必需變強 像神一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.74,0:08:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像神一樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算在遙遠的異國流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是要想辦法回來島原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.78,0:08:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後保護大家\N這些被虐待的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是武藤時貞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.03,0:09:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個天主教的混蛋\N相信異國神的叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃 翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.34,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.71,0:09:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍…將來…一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要成為島原人民的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽 振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.74,0:09:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.41,0:09:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍 小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.51,0:09:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.81,0:09:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些人真笨 信什麼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.12,0:10:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拋棄信仰就可以活命了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.79,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然因此忍受酷刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為神拋棄自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.76,0:10:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拋棄就拋棄啊\N反正他們的生命連條蟲都不值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 他們就照他們的教義\N快樂的上天國吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.07,0:10:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有活著的 這女人命真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.04,0:10:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看要怎麼辦？\N正好可以散心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手 不准對媽媽下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准碰她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小子好像也不要命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.39,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.39,0:10:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐 我來接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.17,0:10:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 船在那邊等著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.15,0:11:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去只會拖累你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就帶著這兩個孩子逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧 翔伍 小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 媽媽也要跟大家一起走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.69,0:11:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍 你不聽媽的話了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是留下媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.17,0:11:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,膽小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.84,0:11:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是將來要領導許多人的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拋棄小小的憐憫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必需變強 像鋼鐵一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.58,0:11:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死在這裏的話\N島原人民的希望就毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要逃 翔伍\N而且要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小夜 這個你拿著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵衛 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.17,0:11:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.44,0:12:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就好 翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要好好保護小夜\N保護小夜啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.64,0:13:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍 你要變強 像神一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.68,0:13:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是將來要領導許多人的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拋棄小小的憐憫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一天你一定要回來島原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.72,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後保護大家\N這些被虐待的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要變強 我一定要變強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不屈服於任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.87,0:13:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何人都不能踐踏我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要成為神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為神 回來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.51,0:13:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護這裏被欺凌的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.06,0:14:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很快就可以去天國了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去爸爸媽媽的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是神的祝福呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼都別說了 別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.55,0:14:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你死的\N我一定要守住你的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.13,0:14:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村你怎麼有辦法這麼快\N一點也不像失明的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是跟隨小操的足音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.91,0:14:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,足音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且從大家的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.78,0:15:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隱約也可以\N感覺到周圍有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.48,0:15:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說…\N我們都成了你的眼睛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.36,0:15:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉 果然不是常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.74,0:15:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有船…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.38,0:15:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的 在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.59,0:15:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是山東 荷蘭領事館的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨夜我也有看到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼他會在這裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.83,0:15:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可能是被利用了 應該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被這個王國的幹部之一\N傀王所利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.64,0:15:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 大有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.41,0:15:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按照我收集到的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王這個人其實在德川時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.28,0:16:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就被我們御庭番眾列為\N最重要危險人物而盯梢著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番眾也…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳教師傀王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他母親是隱藏的天主教徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時受到幕府鎮壓\N渡海到大陸去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大陸生下傀王過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.50,0:16:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王不知生父是誰\N一個人在地獄掙扎生存下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.07,0:16:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他詛咒奪走自己國籍的\N日本這個國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿懷怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.41,0:16:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁著幕末的混亂時期\N偷偷在九州登陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.75,0:16:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從此就虎視眈眈\N等待向這個國家報仇的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王的本質\N似乎跟天草翔伍相差很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.94,0:17:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是信號 他在送信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.31,0:17:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.32,0:17:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 只有可能是軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.32,0:17:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.97,0:17:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐 您在這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.37,0:17:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,源右衛門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您果然在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.81,0:17:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐 我想報告您一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼晚…到底有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.69,0:17:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那絕對是您的項鏈\N不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的項鏈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在傀王大人那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的沒騙我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我說幾次才懂\N你這個石頭腦袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.70,0:18:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的天使的項鏈\N被金髮的男人拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.98,0:18:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你說的話是真的\N項鏈可能在傀王大人那裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.88,0:18:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才問你\N走哪條路才可以找到傀王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問事情不夠禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.32,0:18:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 你別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.02,0:18:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.49,0:18:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.90,0:18:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那地方有什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你們的王國耶\N你不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.94,0:18:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是去年才從大陸過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.31,0:18:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方是\N傀王大人幾年前就建立的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王拿走我的項鏈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.02,0:20:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.52,0:20:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍 這是他的瀕死之圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明早這張圖會成為現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.01,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王 你想背叛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.75,0:20:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背叛？我打一開始就在想\N要如何讓你們兄妹死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明早聖靈的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.79,0:20:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救世主會如這張圖所畫的升天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.99,0:20:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是打動民眾心靈的\N傳說中的死法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.90,0:20:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後我成為\N傳佈他的教導的大司教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳佈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍的預言書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.91,0:21:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面寫了很多\N令信徒感激涕零的預言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救世主死後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.62,0:21:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信徒們\N應該會發誓絕對服從吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥並沒有寫預言書啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 是我寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.76,0:21:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下永遠的預言書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍成為名符其實\N不會毀滅的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時相信會有數萬民眾\N哭嚎著為他而戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.90,0:21:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂民推翻這個國家\N政權落入荷蘭的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.61,0:21:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我成為殖民地之王\N日本徹底滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.01,0:21:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我冒瀆這個國家\N埋葬它 達成心願的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.02,0:21:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王呀 你太會胡說八道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莊三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.76,0:21:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的 聖母小姐\N我不會讓這種人得逞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.37,0:22:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道你這樣的怪物\N末路是通往哪裏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.14,0:22:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就親自來\N把你打進地獄的血池裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.75,0:22:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.32,0:22:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個景觀好看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.65,0:22:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.55,0:22:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是惡魔 神決不會原諒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.89,0:22:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥不會被你殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.66,0:22:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐\N下次在天國見面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.80,0:22:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傀王

